----------------------------------
* AWS IAM Root User Best Practices 
----------------------------------

- Enable Multi-Factor Authentication. ig, microsoft authenticator
- Do not use root account for daily tasks and create an administrative user
- Delete or rotate access key
- We can create upto 2 Access Keys for AWS Root account
- Keep email account secure which is associated with your root account
- Use "ACCOUNT ALIAS" (ig agneypateldotinfo thing)
